meta.title: Rock Paper Scissors - Play Online with Friends

meta.name: description
meta.content: Do you have a dispute with your friend? Resolve it online! If you just want to spend some time, try to fight a random stranger.
Rock Paper Scissors - Play Online with Friends
Rock paper scissors is a simple and interesting game. Many of us used to play it in a school to resolve disputes or just for fun.
